00:14:25,140 --> 00:14:25,940
Jangan minum.

286
00:14:26,980 --> 00:14:27,660
Buangkan ini.

287
00:14:30,100 --> 00:14:30,740
Selain itu,

288
00:14:31,180 --> 00:14:31,980
